---
// Purpose-Built Capabilities section for Property Management industry page
---

<section id="capabilities" class="cre-capabilities-section">
  <div class="cre-capabilities-container">
    <span class="section-label">PURPOSE-BUILT CAPABILITIES</span>
    <h2 class="cre-capabilities-headline">
      Property management systems engineered for your workflow
    </h2>

    <div class="cre-capabilities-grid">
      <!-- Deal Sourcing -->
      <div class="cre-capability-card">
        <div class="cre-capability-icon">
          <img src="/logos/intelio-icon-1.webp" alt="Tenant Management" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="cre-capability-title">Tenant Management</h3>
        <p class="cre-capability-description">
          Centralized tenant database that tracks lease information, communication history, and payment records in one place. Automated tenant onboarding reduces move-in time while ensuring all documentation is collected and stored securely.
        </p>
        <div class="cre-includes-section">
          <strong>INCLUDES:</strong>
          <ul class="cre-includes-list">
            <li>Centralized tenant database</li>
            <li>Automated lease tracking and renewal alerts</li>
            <li>Tenant communication portal</li>
            <li>Document management and storage</li>
            <li>Automated onboarding workflows</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Underwriting -->
      <div class="cre-capability-card">
        <div class="cre-capability-icon">
          <img src="/logos/intelio-icon-5.webp" alt="Maintenance & Work Orders" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="cre-capability-title">Maintenance & Work Orders</h3>
        <p class="cre-capability-description">
          Intelligent maintenance management that tracks work orders, coordinates vendor schedules, and surfaces maintenance issues before they become emergencies. Preventive maintenance workflows reduce costly emergency repairs.
        </p>
        <div class="cre-includes-section">
          <strong>INCLUDES:</strong>
          <ul class="cre-includes-list">
            <li>Work order management and tracking</li>
            <li>Vendor coordination and scheduling</li>
            <li>Preventive maintenance alerts</li>
            <li>Maintenance cost analytics</li>
            <li>Emergency response prioritization</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Portfolio Analytics -->
      <div class="cre-capability-card">
        <div class="cre-capability-icon">
          <img src="/logos/intelio-icon-6.webp" alt="Financial Management" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="cre-capability-title">Financial Management</h3>
        <p class="cre-capability-description">
          Automated financial tracking that consolidates rent payments, expenses, and vendor invoices across all properties. Real-time visibility into income, expenses, and profitability by property.
        </p>
        <div class="cre-includes-section">
          <strong>INCLUDES:</strong>
          <ul class="cre-includes-list">
            <li>Rent collection tracking and reminders</li>
            <li>Expense management and reconciliation</li>
            <li>Property-level financial reporting</li>
            <li>Cash flow forecasting</li>
            <li>Investor/owner reporting automation</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Investor Reporting -->
      <div class="cre-capability-card">
        <div class="cre-capability-icon">
          <img src="/logos/intelio-icon-2.webp" alt="Tenant Communication" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="cre-capability-title">Tenant Communication</h3>
        <p class="cre-capability-description">
          Unified communication platform that manages tenant requests, maintenance notifications, and rent payment reminders through their preferred channels. Reduces lost messages and ensures urgent issues escalate appropriately.
        </p>
        <div class="cre-includes-section">
          <strong>INCLUDES:</strong>
          <ul class="cre-includes-list">
            <li>Multi-channel communication (email, SMS, portal)</li>
            <li>Automated rent payment reminders</li>
            <li>Maintenance issue escalation</li>
            <li>Request tracking and response SLA monitoring</li>
            <li>Communication history and documentation</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Buyer Profile Management -->
      <div class="cre-capability-card">
        <div class="cre-capability-icon">
          <img src="/logos/intelio-icon-3.webp" alt="Property Performance Analytics" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="cre-capability-title">Property Performance Analytics</h3>
        <p class="cre-capability-description">
          Real-time visibility into occupancy rates, average rents, maintenance costs, and tenant satisfaction by property. Identify underperforming units and opportunities to optimize pricing or reduce costs.
        </p>
        <div class="cre-includes-section">
          <strong>INCLUDES:</strong>
          <ul class="cre-includes-list">
            <li>Occupancy and rent tracking</li>
            <li>Tenant turnover analysis</li>
            <li>Maintenance cost by property and type</li>
            <li>Rent collection metrics</li>
            <li>Performance benchmarking</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Market Intelligence -->
      <div class="cre-capability-card">
        <div class="cre-capability-icon">
          <img src="/logos/intelio-icon-7.webp" alt="Lease & Compliance Management" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="cre-capability-title">Lease & Compliance Management</h3>
        <p class="cre-capability-description">
          Automated lease tracking, renewal alerts, and compliance documentation storage. Never miss a lease renewal, rent increase deadline, or compliance requirement.
        </p>
        <div class="cre-includes-section">
          <strong>INCLUDES:</strong>
          <ul class="cre-includes-list">
            <li>Lease renewal alerts and workflow</li>
            <li>Automated rent increase scheduling</li>
            <li>Compliance requirement tracking</li>
            <li>Document version control and storage</li>
            <li>Legal hold management</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .cre-capabilities-section {
    background: #0052CC;
    color: #ffffff;
    width: 100vw;
    margin: 0;
    margin-left: calc(-50vw + 50%);
    padding: clamp(40px, 5vw, 60px) 24px;
  }

  .cre-capabilities-container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .section-label {
    display: block;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .cre-capabilities-headline {
    font-family: 'Figtree', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(40px, 5vw, 56px);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.2;
    color: #ffffff;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .cre-capabilities-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 20px;
    margin-top: 24px;
  }

  .cre-capability-card {
    background: transparent;
    border: 3px solid #ffffff;
    padding: 32px 24px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .cre-capability-icon {
    width: 120px;
    height: 120px;
    margin: 0 auto 24px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .cre-capability-icon img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: contain;
    filter: brightness(0) invert(1);
  }

  .cre-capability-title {
    font-family: 'Figtree', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 600;
    line-height: 1.3;
    color: #ffffff;
    margin: 0 0 12px 0;
  }

  .cre-capability-description {
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
    margin: 0 0 16px 0;
  }

  .cre-includes-section {
    margin-top: 16px;
  }

  .cre-includes-section strong {
    font-size: 11px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .cre-includes-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .cre-includes-list li {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
    padding: 4px 0 4px 16px;
    position: relative;
    line-height: 1.5;
    text-align: left;
  }

  .cre-includes-list li::before {
    content: "â€¢";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .cre-capabilities-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }

    .cre-capability-icon {
      width: 100px;
      height: 100px;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .cre-capabilities-section {
      padding: clamp(20px, 3vw, 40px) 24px;
    }

    .cre-capabilities-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .cre-capability-card {
      padding: 28px 20px;
      border: 2px solid #ffffff;
    }

    .cre-capability-icon {
      width: 80px;
      height: 80px;
      margin: 0 auto 20px;
    }

    .cre-capability-title {
      font-size: 15px;
    }

    .cre-capability-description {
      font-size: 13px;
    }

    .cre-includes-list li {
      font-size: 12px;
    }
  }
</style>

